    "They are responsible for the content's integrity, ensuring AI-generated text is accurate and free of bias or errors.",
    "AI tools, such as ChatGPT or LLMs, cannot be authors because they cannot take responsibility for the work.",
    "Authors using AI for writing, image production, or data analysis must be transparent about its use and fully accountable for the manuscript's content, liable for any ethical breaches.",
